description._content: Collection: Human Ecology Historical Photographs Title: Child Health Organization: Two views of the ''Health Fairy,'' who appeared at Ithaca High School in 1920 under the co-sponsorship of the Child Health Organization and local groups. She was employed directly by the C.H.O., which enlisted co-sponsors in places where she appeared. Troy photo. Collection #23-2-749, item PR-PO-23 Div. Rare & Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library Persistent URI: http://hdl.handle.net/1813.001/5w8w There are no known U.S. copyright restrictions on this image.
